Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back against the wall... I \Nmean, how could I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This wasn't supposed to \Nhappen," I keep denying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:01:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just disappear... \NI can't stand myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping around, spouting lies, \Ngrieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold on desperately to these \Nfeelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does this stupid \Nguilt refuse to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffocate under its weight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clinging selfishly to \Nthe hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:04.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4: Peter Grill and Bathing Etiquette
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pure evil...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Peter-san handle that \Ncreature all on his own...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you lay a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ON LUVELLIA-SENPAI?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man you see before you is the\Nstrongest warrior on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He totally kicked that thing's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, talk about awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one stands a chance against Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lookin' at the strongest \Nman alive, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Right you are, Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This merely reaffirms our mission to incorporate his
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,genetic superiority into our bloodline at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren'tcha glad we hightailed it to the Warriors Guild as soon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as we caught wind of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing such extraordinary \Ncombat prowess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Horny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This serves as proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd be completely lost without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill! Peter Grill! Peter Grill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill! Peter Grill! Peter Grill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is... awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, Luvellia-senpai \Nsuffered only minor injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the local townspeople were grateful\Nto us for ridding them of the creature, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this raging boner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover adrenaline from the battle, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's been several hours. There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the aftermath...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dude rescued an entire village\Nand yet he's still so humble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real heroes don't walk around \Nactin' all high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have something to do with\Nthe spell that Elf cast on me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you've grown since \Nwe last met, Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess:\NYou're beginning to regret your foolish decision
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to refuse an arrangement with the\Nexquisite Vegan Eldoriel, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason I've been \Npitchin' a tent is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely, a forbidden curse passed\Ndown amongst my brethren:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Eternal Erection."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subjects upon whom the curse is cast experience
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a sense of insatiable arousal in their nether regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, this causes damage \Nto the penile tissues...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resulting in the permanent\Ninability to pop a pocket rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAAAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a major function of your manhood\Nand turning into a dusty old geezer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at such a young age sounds \Nawfully miserable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, not that! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't quite hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please break the curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMN ELF...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, I shall break the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once this type of magic has been cast,\Nthere's only one way to reverse its effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must deposit your juices...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spilling your sweet gravy inside \Nof me is the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly expect me to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai is the only woman for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it WAS you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a familiar voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hot spring is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the water is so soothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my cuts and \Nbruises healing as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard the legends \Nsurrounding this resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wh-what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village itself is famous \Nfor its hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this particular spring is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It flows from a special source and is\Nsaid to have a rather fascinating effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those who soak themselves in these mysterious\Nwaters shall be blessed with children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could join me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could test out the effects \Nof the hot spring together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-SAY WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?! Hallucinating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHE'S... asking ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd see the day...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't progressed towards any sort of\Nphysical intimacy other than holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime chance\Nto take things to the next level!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My crown jewels are practically\Non the verge of exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspense is killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely CANNOT afford \Nto waste this opportunity...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a bit sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, the others might see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps if we took a bath and \Nsaid a prayer together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stork would descend \Nupon us from the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our future child in tow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be pleading for mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something you wish to ask of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End this torture and take my load!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any shred of self-respect \NI had left as a warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been smashed up into little pieces...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely doing what's necessary\Nto protect my future with Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, it's time to drop \Nthis pathetic charade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready when you are, Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't count...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even CLOSE to cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got some pretty good moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you were my \Nbiggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till death do us part, \Nlet's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And find no one like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sight of you fills my heart with joy
